    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for the MRL 2 / Class II / medium model influence profile. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 across all five operating points supports the regulatory submission claim that the subject device does not produce greater hemolysis than the predicate device. The credibility evidence package is assessed as sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision.",
